Database::Cassandra::Client
=============

DESCRIPTION

This is glue for Cassandra C/C++ Driver library version 1.0.

See https://github.com/datastax/cpp-driver/tree/1.0


INSTALLATION

Please, before install this module make Cassandra library version 1.0.

Just follow the usual procedure:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


REPORTING BUGS

